data.description: WELCOME TO THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME. Located in the beautiful Carriage Pointe community! This home features an open floorplan, lovely kitchen with ample counter space, appliances and tile flooring throughout the main living areas. Positioned on a quiet street with mature trees, this concrete block home features. This beautiful home provides two different access to the covered patio and private backyard. Primary suite is separated from the secondary bedrooms. This home includes a two-car garage for your convenience, providing both parking and additional storage. Key Home updates on the property include exterior painting 2021, picket fence 2020, SOD 2022, Hurricane Shutters 2022, Rain gutters in 2022, Laminate flooring and Lanai enclosed in 2021, Halo UV Light Air Conditioner System in 2023 THE SELLER REPLACE A NEW CANOPY FOR THE OUTDOOR GAZEBO.  Carriage Pointe features a clubhouse, Community pool, playground, fitness center, basketball and tennis court. All of these amenities are easily accessible using the endless sidewalks found throughout the community allowing you to enjoy biking, dog-walking, and jogging located near grocery stores, hospitals, schools, restaurants, parks, easy interstate, crosstown access to downtown, airport, beaches, and many other amenities. Apollo Beach Nature Preserve is 8 miles away as well as the Apollo Beach Park which has a dog park, skate park, splash pad, and playground. There's more, just 2 miles away is a movie theater, a variety of restaurants, a car wash, and a Walmart Supercenter, Sam's Club, Publix, Lowes. Many charter and magnet schools are nearby as well! Not only is the home fabulous, but Great location also gives you easy access to Hwy 301, Hwy 41, and I-75 to travel to downtown Tampa, and just minutes to Tampa Bay, Brandon, and Florida's world-famous beaches or Disney in Orlando. DO NOT miss this great opportunity.
